Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}防止危机爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}危机吗
